<Mod Name="Winter Warfare 2024">
    <Author>rast</Author>
    <Description>Who said there's no New Year on Mars? It's only twice as rare: once in 687 days. So Martians have to party twice as hard!

Arm yourselves with snowballs and explosive gifts for proper celebration.
	
Best played on Frost, Downfall, Pinnacle or Fortress.

Changes:
* Replaced hand grenade with snowball: 2 direct hits to kill, also has splash damage. Snowball is selected as default weapon
* Replaced remote charge model with gift box. Your friends will have to stick to these
* Replaced singularity bomb model with VOGEL gift bag. No holidays without plastic bricks!
* Thermobaric fireworks combined with a homemade christmas tree
	</Description>
